==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Among people, in the heavens.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén jiān tiān shàng

===Idiom===
'''[[人间]][[天]][[上]]''' 

# Describes two people who are separated by a great distance.
# Heaven on earth.

===Alternate forms===
[[人間天上]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[天上人间]]

